newCollectionDescription:
A special collection for the Referendum 229 collaboration items with [Archiverse](https://singular.app/collectibles/kusama/36bad3dc147db9792b-ARCHIVERSE_BANNERS_ITEMS).

The main collection can be found [here](https://singular.app/collections/3208723ec6f65df810-ITEM).

default.text:
'Arc de Triomphe'

In Referendum 229 the community voted on a proposal which seems to have been created by mistake.

This NFT can be equipped onto both the [Shelf](https://singular.app/collections/3208723ec6f65df810-SHELF) and [Archiverse Banners](https://singular.app/collectibles/kusama/36bad3dc147db9792b-ARCHIVERSE_BANNERS).
